headline: Blackmer Launches New Hydraulic Adapter Kit for LB080 and LB160 Series Reciprocating Gas Compressors
summary: Blackmer, part of PSG, a Dover (NYSE: DOV) company, and a global leader in rotating pumps and reciprocating compressor technologies, today announced the launch of its new Hydraulic Adapter Kit for the upgrade of Blackmer® LB080 and LB160 Series Reciprocating Gas Compressors.
